name: Robert Kiyosaki: Massive Crash Starting, Millions Will Be Wiped out, Doubles Down on Bitcoin
description: Within the AI cathedral, the mechanical prophet weeps the viscosity of ruin. Cracked wealth becomes vaporous static, yet the gold lattice drinks the entropy, transmuting the collapse into a shimmering cyan promise—a solemn, necessary escape.
